1
00:01:29,470 --> 00:01:33,120
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:36,250
[Episode 14]

3
00:01:36,840 --> 00:01:38,190
[Qunhua Hall]

4
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,180
Judging from how they look,

5
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:17,150
I don't think they're much better than us.

6
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:19,610
One, two, three, four.

7
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,240
Plus President Wan,

8
00:02:21,270 --> 00:02:23,310
there are eight of them in total.

9
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:24,720
But we only have seven people.

10
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:26,760
Will our formation look bad?

11
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,760
What are you afraid of?

12
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:30,690
I think they're just putting on a front.

13
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:14,600
Are you sure...
they're just putting on a front?

14
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:18,390
I'm afraid we can't defeat them
on pure ability.

15
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:19,360
In my opinion,

16
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,360
we're definitely going to lose.

17
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,290
How come...

18
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,140
those two girls

19
00:03:25,160 --> 00:03:26,900
look familiar to me?

20
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,560
They look familiar to me too.

21
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,360
It's you lot!

22
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:36,900
Run!

23
00:03:44,450 --> 00:03:45,570
P-President Wan.

24
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:49,760
If you want to watch, do it openly.

25
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:52,200
Why do you have to be so sneaky?

26
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:55,400
President Wan,
they've always been like this—unruly

27
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,360
and up to no good.

28
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,520
How have you been, ladies?

29
00:03:58,760 --> 00:04:01,850
Little did I expect
to meet you two here again.

30
00:04:01,870 --> 00:04:03,260
It's all thanks to you.

31
00:04:03,290 --> 00:04:04,240
You didn't sign your name.

32
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,600
So we became the champion.

33
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,860
And we reached here effortlessly.

34
00:04:06,860 --> 00:04:07,900
The two of you are

35
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,440
so smug after taking advantage of others.

36
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,440
It's enough that you aren't grateful,

37
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:14,970
but to kick us when we're down
is just too much.

38
00:04:16,890 --> 00:04:17,750
President Wan,

39
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,040
they were shamelessly peeking at us.

40
00:04:20,040 --> 00:04:22,560
Such sneaky skulkers deserve punishment.

41
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:25,400
We'll teach them a lesson
on President Wan's behalf.

42
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:26,730
Don't you dare touch us!

43
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:27,520
Who are you?

44
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:29,000
How bold of you
for bringing a sharp weapon.

45
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,960
How dare you commit assault
in President Wan's presence!

46
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:31,760
Tu Ya!

47
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,640
You can't do this.

48
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,930
Stop pestering us,

49
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,690
or I won't go easy on you.

50
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,850
Tu Ya!

51
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:42,730
-President Wan!
-President Wan!

52
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,659
President Wan,

53
00:04:49,670 --> 00:04:50,950
our behavior today

54
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:52,360
was indeed inappropriate.

55
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,890
If that caused any offense,

56
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,360
I'd like to apologize to you,

57
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:58,920
President Wan, and everyone present here.

58
00:04:59,960 --> 00:05:00,680
President Wan,

59
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,460
don't be fooled by her sweet talk.

60
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:04,980
Those who break the rules like you lot

61
00:05:05,080 --> 00:05:06,240
-deserve severe punishment!
-deserve severe punishment!

62
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,040
Enough.

63
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:11,260
All this yelling and arguing
is not fit for decent company!

64
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,460
Since they have apologized,

65
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,800
let's stop pursuing the matter.

66
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:28,200
Hurry up and go prepare for the match.

67
00:05:28,430 --> 00:05:29,940
-President Wan!
-President Wan!

68
00:05:29,940 --> 00:05:31,700
I mean, break it up.

69
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,380
-Yes.
-Yes.

70
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:43,300
Thank you, President Wan.

71
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:48,409
[High Art]

72
00:05:49,409 --> 00:05:50,450
Oh, no.

73
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,360
I really can't do this anymore.

74
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,900
It's like my waist is breaking.

75
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,920
My legs!

76
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,440
I can't keep this up.

77
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:03,720
Please spare me.

78
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:04,650
Pace yourself.

79
00:06:04,670 --> 00:06:06,760
Hang in there.

80
00:06:12,150 --> 00:06:15,480
Why doesn't she need to practice?

81
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,900
For a martial arts practitioner,

82
00:06:20,900 --> 00:06:22,500
these are just basic skills.

83
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:29,410
Look how cocky she is.

84
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:30,840
Come on.

85
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:33,330
Press my legs harder.

86
00:06:34,370 --> 00:06:37,960
[High Art]

87
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:00,180
That flute is from your hometown, right?

88
00:07:01,050 --> 00:07:02,250
Don't be nervous.

89
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:04,850
I'm here to send you a handsome gift.

90
00:07:06,500 --> 00:07:07,360
President Wan,

91
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,430
we are on different sides.

92
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:11,490
We have nothing to talk about.

93
00:07:11,490 --> 00:07:14,550
No wonder you could be a centurion
in the Chilian Tribe.

94
00:07:14,570 --> 00:07:15,510
It seems

95
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:18,500
I'd better present a big enough gift.

96
00:07:19,290 --> 00:07:20,360
Cut the crap.

97
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:21,740
Just speak your mind.

98
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:22,540
Fine.

99
00:07:23,320 --> 00:07:25,230
I'm looking to make a deal with you.

100
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:27,940
As long as you help me
fight against Nan Yanzhi,

101
00:07:27,970 --> 00:07:29,540
I promise I will

102
00:07:29,570 --> 00:07:31,570
let you go back to the Chilian Tribe.

103
00:07:35,270 --> 00:07:38,180
[High Art]

104
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:51,740
All guiding rings for the voice-keepers
in Lingya Tower

105
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:54,560
are sized
according to their left ring fingers.

106
00:07:54,580 --> 00:07:56,240
As for the size of this ring...

107
00:07:58,790 --> 00:07:59,710
See?

108
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:04,480
It shows that the owner of this ring
has much slenderer fingers than I do.

109
00:08:06,330 --> 00:08:08,860
I don't find anything
noticeably suspicious

110
00:08:09,130 --> 00:08:11,650
about these girls' speech and behavior.

111
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,390
But as Master said,

112
00:08:14,780 --> 00:08:16,510
I must not easily trust anyone.

113
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:59,920
People who have worked as voice-keepers
stay alert all the time.

114
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:03,520
She can't possibly miss
such an obvious assassination attempt.

115
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:19,840
Could she be... on the Red Team?

116
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,640
Who are you?

117
00:10:07,310 --> 00:10:08,430
Master.

118
00:10:09,740 --> 00:10:10,940
What brings you here?

119
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:13,720
The Tower Master suddenly ordered me
to deliver a letter for him.

120
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,210
I have a bad feeling

121
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,990
that someone might harm you.

122
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:29,140
Put this on to protect yourself.

123
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:33,980
Isn't it the filigree bangle
I gave you as a gift?

124
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,940
What exactly is going on?

125
00:10:36,050 --> 00:10:37,310
I'm still investigating it.

126
00:10:37,310 --> 00:10:39,890
Meanwhile, I'll try to keep you safe.

127
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,360
Master, I...

128
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,840
Now, go and get some sleep.

129
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,490
Don't cause extra trouble.

130
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:45,940
But...

131
00:10:45,970 --> 00:10:46,720
Just go.

132
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,260
Nan Yanzhi.

133
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,480
What a surprise...

134
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:24,160
that you're acquainted
with the mute servant.

135
00:11:26,400 --> 00:11:27,640
Why are you like a cat,

136
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:29,480
walking around without a sound?

137
00:11:30,510 --> 00:11:31,720
Nan Yanzhi,

138
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,710
your death is not far off.

139
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:42,960
Are you going to kill me?

140
00:11:43,590 --> 00:11:44,920
I am not the one planning

141
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,320
to kill you.

142
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:50,370
Today, Wan Hongliu approached me
in private,

143
00:11:50,660 --> 00:11:52,720
asking me to join her in fighting you.

144
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:55,540
At this time of year,
people in the Chilian Tribe

145
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:57,630
would slaughter cattle and sheep

146
00:11:57,930 --> 00:11:59,160
to celebrate the turn of the year.

147
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,320
At night,

148
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:03,210
everyone would gather around the bonfire,
singing, dancing,

149
00:12:03,210 --> 00:12:04,540
and drinking heartily.

150
00:12:06,390 --> 00:12:08,250
Now is the perfect time, isn't it?

151
00:12:08,680 --> 00:12:10,140
As long as agree to help me,

152
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:12,950
you'll just be in time
to go home for the event.

153
00:12:17,290 --> 00:12:20,620
It's a shame
that all my tribespeople are gone now.

154
00:12:22,530 --> 00:12:23,980
At this time last year,

155
00:12:24,010 --> 00:12:25,810
there was a traitor in our tribe.

156
00:12:26,130 --> 00:12:28,030
All my fellow tribe members were killed.

157
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:28,750
And I was...

158
00:12:29,300 --> 00:12:31,830
falsely accused
of colluding with the enemy,

159
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:34,050
which reduced me to this state.

160
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:39,010
Therefore,

161
00:12:39,830 --> 00:12:41,230
in my whole life,

162
00:12:41,600 --> 00:12:43,040
there's nothing I hate

163
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:45,420
more than traitors.

164
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:50,840
What we the Chilian tribespeople
despise most

165
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:53,930
is such backstabbing and shady schemes.

166
00:12:54,040 --> 00:12:55,080
Tu Ya, I was simply...

167
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:55,640
Alright.

168
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:58,280
It's not safe to stay here for long.

169
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,330
We'd better hurry back.

170
00:12:59,330 --> 00:13:00,170
Tu Ya.

171
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,070
Tu Ya, thank you.

172
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,840
I once said
we would leave this place together.

173
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:05,480
I believe we can make it happen.

174
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:08,160
Save that speech after we survive
tomorrow's death match.

175
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:09,240
You have fought many battles,

176
00:13:09,240 --> 00:13:10,220
so you certainly understand

177
00:13:10,220 --> 00:13:11,510
that there are always opportunities

178
00:13:11,510 --> 00:13:13,150
for us till the last moment comes.

179
00:13:13,150 --> 00:13:14,350
Opportunities?

180
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,880
Under my watch,

181
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:19,400
you will not have one single opportunity.

182
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,520
Everyone,

183
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:43,550
welcome to the Great Hall of Elegance.

184
00:13:43,940 --> 00:13:46,540
The first round is a dance competition.

185
00:13:46,830 --> 00:13:48,100
The Red and Blue Teams

186
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:51,300
will each finish a dance
to a provided tune.

187
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:55,730
The winning team will be decided
based on the quality of the performances.

188
00:13:55,730 --> 00:13:56,770
The first round

189
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:59,080
officially begins now.

190
00:14:32,760 --> 00:14:34,690
Lingya Tower is truly

191
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,620
a place of hidden talents.

192
00:14:36,680 --> 00:14:38,560
Look at the dance of these beauties.

193
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:41,030
They are all graceful and charming.

194
00:14:41,050 --> 00:14:43,620
Even the top courtesans
of the Moon House in the capital

195
00:14:43,620 --> 00:14:45,550
might not dance better than them.

196
00:14:45,570 --> 00:14:46,870
I agree.

197
00:14:46,900 --> 00:14:48,790
The Red Team is going to win!

198
00:14:51,360 --> 00:14:52,340
My Lady.

199
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:13,760
Look how cocky they are.

200
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,790
It's your turn.

201
00:15:20,350 --> 00:15:21,900
I forgot to tell you something.

202
00:15:21,900 --> 00:15:24,620
The girl who causes the team
to lose at the end

203
00:15:25,180 --> 00:15:26,650
will be killed.

204
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:27,900
Killed?

205
00:15:27,930 --> 00:15:29,620
You didn't say that at the beginning.

206
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:31,700
This last-minute statement
shouldn't be valid, right?

207
00:15:31,700 --> 00:15:34,560
President Wan, you're informing us
of a new rule just when our turn arrives.

208
00:15:34,560 --> 00:15:36,540
This is meant to disturb
our peace of mind, isn't it?

209
00:15:36,540 --> 00:15:39,410
If I had kept it from you
till the end of the competition,

210
00:15:39,410 --> 00:15:41,410
it would be even worse, wouldn't it?

211
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,010
On this floor managed by me,

212
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:45,370
only one person will die in each round.

213
00:15:47,670 --> 00:15:50,070
You're better off here than anywhere else.

214
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:00,820
Oh no.

215
00:16:01,050 --> 00:16:02,470
What's the second move?

216
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:04,340
Oh, stop talking, Dao.

217
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,690
You're causing me to forget stuff too.

218
00:16:05,690 --> 00:16:06,970
Isn't our captain right ahead?

219
00:16:06,970 --> 00:16:08,170
Just follow her lead.

220
00:16:22,700 --> 00:16:23,830
Man!

221
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,240
That was an honest mistake.

222
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:27,130
I beg for another chance,
President Wan! I...

